node.text:
Craving for this yummy & popular Nasi lemak at Bedok area ! 
All their ingredients freshly fried on the spot & run out fast fast ! 
Chili was super spicy shiok shiok !
Always long Q & minimum waiting time from 15 mins to 30 mins.
FYI sold out by 1pm ...😉!
🏢Hon Ni Kitchen
216 Bedok North Street 1
#01-07
Singapore 460216
